                        </tbody>
                      </table>
                    </div>
                    <p class="mt-2 text-[11px] italic text-slate-500">
                      Eight variants, two distinct Google walls. The strongest pure-Playwright cloak (H)
                      clears the fingerprint check but still triggers reCAPTCHA. Beyond H the next move is
                      no longer a cloaking change — it's a vision model (AIVA) or a one-time human captcha
                      solve to bootstrap a storage-state replay.
                    </p>
                  </>
                )}

                <details class="group mt-6 rounded-md border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50">
                  <summary class="flex cursor-pointer select-none items-center justify-between px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 hover:bg-slate-100">
